{
  "_comment": "Ryazhenka Updater download catalogue. Three URL shapes are supported by source/list_download_tab.cpp click handler: (1) direct https URLs for repos with stable asset filenames; (2) '@latest_asset:OWNER/REPO' — resolved at click time via api.github.com, takes first .zip asset of latest release (fallback assets[0]); (3) '@download_to:<DEST>:<URL_or_marker>' — single-file download to DEST path, no extract, used for .ovl and standalone .nro; (4) '@reorg_ppsspp:OWNER/REPO' — like @latest_asset but reorganises after extract (moves PPSSPP_GL.nro to /switch/ and assets/ to /switch/ppsspp/).",
